<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?> <?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="rss.xsl"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"> <channel> <title>基岩文档</title><description>Minecraft基岩版开发文档</description><link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/</link><atom:link href="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /> <docs>https://github.com/MiemieMethod/bedrock-docs</docs><language>zh</language> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 02:34:51 -0000</pubDate> <lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 02:34:51 -0000</lastBuildDate> <ttl>1440</ttl> <generator>MkDocs RSS plugin - v1.19.0</generator> <image> <url>None</url> <title>基岩文档</title> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/</link> </image> <item> <title>技术</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;技术&lt;/h1&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 02:37:44 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/category/技术.png" type="image/png" length="10425" /> </item> <item> <title>2024</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;2024&lt;/h1&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 02:37:44 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/archive/2024.png" type="image/png" length="12772" /> </item> <item> <title>JSON共用构件</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;JSON共用构件&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JSON共用构件（JSON Shared Construct）&lt;/strong&gt;是附加包系统中可复用的、跨多处系统通用的标准化JSON结构体。这些构件不以独立文件的形式存在，而是内嵌于各类定义文件的特定字段中，用于简洁地描述方块、物品或数值范围等通用概念。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;方块描述符&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;**方块描述符（Bl...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/addon/json-construct/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/addon/json-construct/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/addon/json-construct.png" type="image/png" length="16804" /> </item> <item> <title>开启实验性玩法</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;开启实验性玩法&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;在Minecraft基岩版中，实验性玩法通常可以在创建世界或编辑世界设置时直接开启。对于Minecraft教育版、基岩版专用服务器，或者已经创建完成且无法通过界面重新设置的世界，往往需要直接编辑&lt;code&gt;level.dat&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;先备份世界&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// warning | 先备份 编辑`leve...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/help/minecraft/enabling-experimental-features/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/help/minecraft/enabling-experimental-features/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/help/minecraft/enabling-experimental-features.png" type="image/png" length="10639" /> </item> <item> <title>方块与物品问答</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;方块与物品问答（2024/08/30）&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// details-info | 署名信息 - 该页面内容翻译自&lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/blocks-items-qna&#34;&gt;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/blocks-items-qna&lt;/a&gt; - 该...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/blocks-items-qna/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/blocks-items-qna/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/blocks-items-qna.png" type="image/png" length="10639" /> </item> <item> <title>延迟技术预览问答</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;延迟技术预览问答（2024/02/23）&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// details-info | 署名信息 - 该页面内容翻译自&lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/deferred-qna&#34;&gt;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/deferred-qna&lt;/a&gt; - 该页面由[Eas...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/deferred-qna/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/deferred-qna/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/deferred-qna.png" type="image/png" length="10747" /> </item> <item> <title>GameTest问答</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;GameTest问答（2021/08/06）&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// details-info | 署名信息 - 该页面内容翻译自&lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/gametest-qna&#34;&gt;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/gametest-qna&lt;/a&gt; - 该页面由[E...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/gametest-qna/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/gametest-qna/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/gametest-qna.png" type="image/png" length="18951" /> </item> <item> <title>脚本与编辑器问答</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;脚本与编辑器问答（2023/09/22）&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// details-info | 署名信息 - 该页面内容翻译自[https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/scripting-editor-qna](https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/scripting-editor...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/scripting-editor-qna/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/scripting-editor-qna/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/scripting-editor-qna.png" type="image/png" length="10747" /> </item> <item> <title>世界生成问答</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;世界生成问答（2024/11/15）&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;/// details-info | 署名信息 - 该页面内容翻译自&lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/world-gen-qna&#34;&gt;https://wiki.bedrock.dev/meta/world-gen-qna&lt;/a&gt; - 该页面由[Eas...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/world-gen-qna/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 01:04:20 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/world-gen-qna/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/bedrock-wiki/meta/world-gen-qna.png" type="image/png" length="10671" /> </item> <item> <title>表情符号</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;表情符号&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;表情符号（Emoji）&lt;/strong&gt;是基岩版内置的一组Unicode私有使用区（Private Use Area，PUA）字符。游戏会把这些字符渲染为图标或符号，而不是普通文字，因此它们可以在告示牌、书与笔、聊天、物品名称和部分界面文本中充当装饰性或提示性字符。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;概述&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;很多位置都支持直接输入短...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/addon/emojis/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:38:55 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/addon/emojis/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/addon/emojis.png" type="image/png" length="10480" /> </item> <item> <title>输入键</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;输入键&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;输入键（Input Key）&lt;/strong&gt;是基岩版用于显示玩家当前输入方式的文本占位符。输入键会根据玩家当前的控制方案自动替换成对应按键、手柄按钮或触摸图标，因此常用于操作提示、引导文本和界面说明。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;概述&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;输入键通常写在语言文件中，再由游戏在显示时替换为具体图标或按键名称。例如，在过山车结束提示...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/addon/input-keys/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:38:55 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/addon/input-keys/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/addon/input-keys.png" type="image/png" length="10451" /> </item> <item> <title>NetherNet</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;NetherNet&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NetherNet&lt;/strong&gt;是Minecraft基岩版所使用的网络协议之一，基于WebRTC，主要用于Xbox Live会话的多人连接。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;概述&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;基岩版采用多种网络协议栈处理不同来源的连接。其中，&lt;a href=&#34;raknet.md&#34;&gt;RakNet&lt;/a&gt;用于面向公网IP和端口的直接服务器连接（即外部服...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/nethernet/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:38:55 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/nethernet/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/server/nethernet.png" type="image/png" length="13098" /> </item> <item> <title>RakNet</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;RakNet&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RakNet&lt;/strong&gt;是一套跨平台、开源的C++游戏网络引擎，最初由Jenkins Software开发，后移交至Facebook Archive进行维护。Minecraft基岩版将RakNet&lt;strong&gt;（RakNet）&lt;/strong&gt;用作面向外部服务器连接的主要传输层协议。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;概述&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;RakNet基于UD...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/raknet/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:38:55 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/raknet/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/server/raknet.png" type="image/png" length="15158" /> </item> <item> <title>禁用原版粒子</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;禁用原版粒子&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;有时，资源包需要移除或替换原版粒子特效——例如在建立极简画风的材质包时去掉爆炸或魔法粒子，或者在优化性能时彻底停止某些高频粒子的发射。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;推荐做法&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;正确做法是覆盖粒子定义文件，而不是将粒子纹理改为透明。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;将粒子纹理改透明看似有效，但发射器依然正常工作——每次触发时仍然创建粒子...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/disabling-particles/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:16:00 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/disabling-particles/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/addons/data-driven/disabling-particles.png" type="image/png" length="10671" /> </item> <item> <title>AFK检测</title> <description>通过行为包动画控制器检测玩家挂机（AFK）状态，并在进入或离开挂机时执行命令。</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/afk-detector/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:16:00 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/afk-detector/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/afk-detector.png" type="image/png" length="12624" /> </item> <item> <title>死亡触发命令</title> <description>学习在实体死亡时可靠地执行命令的正确方法。</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/death-commands/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:16:00 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/death-commands/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/death-commands.png" type="image/png" length="8345" /> </item> <item> <title>实体触发命令</title> <description>学习如何通过行为包动画控制器让实体在特定时机执行斜杠命令。</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/entity-commands/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:16:00 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/entity-commands/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/entity-commands.png" type="image/png" length="8383" /> </item> <item> <title>复活触发命令</title> <description>学习在玩家复活时执行命令的方法。</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/respawn-commands/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:16:00 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/respawn-commands/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/addons/data-driven/entities/respawn-commands.png" type="image/png" length="8331" /> </item> <item> <title>Molang值转记分板</title> <description>将任意Molang查询或变量的数值读取到实体记分板分数中的高级技巧。</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/misc/molang-to-scoreboard/</link> <pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:16:00 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/misc/molang-to-scoreboard/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/misc/molang-to-scoreboard.png" type="image/png" length="17932" /> </item> <item> <title>自定义盔甲</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;自定义盔甲&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;本篇将带你创建一套完整的自定义盔甲，包含四件套的物品定义、纹理映射、附着物定义以及套装效果。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;h2&gt;盔甲纹理&lt;/h2&gt; &lt;p&gt;基岩版盔甲纹理由两张PNG文件组成：&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;custom_1.png&lt;/code&gt;：头盔、胸甲、靴子的纹理&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;custom_2.png&lt;/code&gt;：护腿的纹理&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;将两张纹理文件放入`RP/textu...&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/items/custom-armor/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 23:27:55 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_rss_created.xml">基岩文档</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/addons/data-driven/items/custom-armor/</guid> <enclosure url="https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/addons/data-driven/items/custom-armor.png" type="image/png" length="10553" /> </item> </channel> </rss>